La Passione  album Chrisa Rea, wydany w listopadzie 1996 roku, zawierajcy ciek dwikow do filmu o tym samym tytule. Autorem scenariusza i producentem filmu by rwnie Chris Rea.

== Lista utworw ==
"La Passione" (Film Theme) - 4:55
"Dov' II Signore?" - 6:04 (vocal Thobias Draper)
"Shirley do You Own a Ferrari?" - 4:43 (vocal Chris Rea & Shirley Bassey)
"Girl in a Sports Car" - 5:16
"When the Grey Skies Turn to Blue" - 3:43
"Horses" - 3:05
"Olive Oil" - 4:26
"Only to Fly" - 5:42
"You Must Follow" - 5:29
"'Disco' la Passione" - 4:57 (vocal Shirley Bassey)
"Dov' II Signore? Pt. 2" - 2:31
"Le Mans" - 3:59